{"id":707,"date":"2022-09-16T15:02:00","date_gmt":"2022-09-16T20:02:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/?p=707"},"modified":"2025-12-09T15:07:41","modified_gmt":"2025-12-09T21:07:41","slug":"pi-kappa-alpha","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/posts\/2022\/2022\/pi-kappa-alpha\/","title":{"rendered":"Pi Kappa Alpha"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>This is part of the <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"918\">Hazing Transparency Report<\/a>, which contains <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#terminology\">terminology definitions<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#rules\">rules defined<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><ul class=\"ua_link-list ua_layout--grid\" >\n<li><a href=\"#fall2022\" class=\"ua_link-list_item\"> Fall 2022<\/a><\/li>\n\n<li><a href=\"#spring2024\" class=\"ua_link-list_item\"> Spring 2024<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-style-elevated is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" id=\"fall2022\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Fall 2022<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<p>Incident: 9\/6\/2022<br>Location: On Campus<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p>Reported: 9\/16\/2022<br>Reported by: GSU Staff, NHQ<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p>Investigation: Joint, initially NHQ-led<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Description<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Pi Kappa Alpha hazed new members through personal servitude, degradation including being sprayed with water and alcohol, physical contact with injuries, forced exercises and line-ups.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Rules Violations<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Article III.B.(2)a. &#8211; Hazing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.B.(2)b. &#8211; Knowledge of Hazing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.A.(4) &#8211; Published Policies<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Findings<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hazing: Calisthenics, Physical Threat; Mental Health Threat<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sanctions<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Disciplinary Probation from 11\/8\/22 to 11\/8\/2024<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Interim measures<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Educational Programs: New member education, Hazing prevention education<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Social event limitations<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Alumni advisory board<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Revision of judicial\/standards<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Executive officer training: Bystander intervention, Risk management, Fire\/health\/safety, Alcohol and drug education, Hazing prevention, Title IX, DEI<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>National council sanctions<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-style-default is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" id=\"spring2024\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Spring 2024<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<p>Incident: Spring 2024 &#8211; Fall 2024<br>Location: On and Off Campus<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p>Reported: 1\/21\/2025<br>Reported by: Hotline Report, Students, Parents<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p>Investigation: GSU-led<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Description<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Pi Kappa Alpha new members were forced or coerced to participate in degrading and illegal activities, physical exercise, and acts of personal servitude. New members were provided and\/or forced or coerced to consume and\/or purchase alcohol and drugs. New members were subjected to phone confiscation\/controlled use and denied privileges.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Rules Violations<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Article III.B.(2)a. &#8211; Hazing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.B.(2)b. &#8211; Hazing Policy<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.A.(4) &#8211; Published Policies<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Findings<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hazing: Calisthenics, personal servitude, degradation, deception, phone confiscation, alcohol, drugs, intimidation, sensory deprivation<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Individuals Responsible: 8<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Arrests<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>None<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sanctions<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Disciplinary Probation through June 23, 2026<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Educational Assessment Fee<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Campus Hazing Speaker<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Chapter and Organizational Education<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Leadership Education (Executive Team, New Member and Recruitment Leadership)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Recruitment Limitations<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Loss of Social Privileges through 10\/2\/2025<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Decreased Social Privileges Fall 2025<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Loss of block seating<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>International Fraternity Sanctions<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Implementation of Wellness and Substance Abuse Action Plan<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fall 2022 Description Pi Kappa Alpha hazed new members through personal servitude, degradation including being sprayed with water and alcohol, physical contact with injuries, forced exercises and line-ups. Spring 2024 Description Pi Kappa Alpha new members were forced or coerced to participate in degrading and illegal activities, physical exercise, and acts of personal servit